@using ZtherApiIntegration.Models.Swatch
@model SwatchListModel

<section id="prints_page" class="clearfix prints_solids_page">
    <div class="info_slider">
        <div class="flexslider">
            <div class="content">
                <ul class="slides">
                    <li>
                        <div class="content">
                            <h1 class="top">Solids</h1>
                            <div class="body">Your work is important to you and your patients.  Your uniform should reflect that as well.  Landau offers a wide range of solid color scrub options to help you look the professional that you are. Providing a great selection of solid colored scrub options for you is key to keeping your work wardrobe fresh and up-to-date. That’s why we look forward to providing our scrubs in new solid color options each season.</div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div class="content">
                            <h2 class="top">Solids</h2>
                            <div class="body">From the more traditional Blue, Green, and White colored scrubs, to something a bit more edgy like Burgundy, Orange, Maroon, Yellow or even Hunter Green scrubs, Landau’s solid color palettes are sure to please. Each Landau color comes in a variety of styles to make the process of finding the right outfit easy.</div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div class="content">
                            <h2 class="top">Solids</h2>
                            <div class="body">Whether you are looking for solid scrubs to coordinate with your group program or for a new pant to coordinate with your prints we have what you’re looking for. Our designers meticulously research color trends to offer a great range of solid colored scrubs and colored lab coats that still keep you looking great every season.</div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div class="content">
                            <h2 class="top">Solids</h2>
                            <div class="body">To help you find the right solid colored scrub for you, just select the solid color you want to quickly find a list of styles that color is available in. Once you select a style you can find out even more detail about the product. At Landau, we want you to look and feel your best, with styles and colors that suit all of your uniform needs.</div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="top_divider"></div>
    <div class="banner solids_banner inner">
        <img class="model" srcset="public/images/prints/solids_banners/model.jpg" />
        <div class="content">
            <div class="inner">
                <span class="top">
                    <img srcset="public/images/prints/solids_banners/banner_text.png" alt="Colorful" />
                </span>
                <span class="middle desktop">
                    Complements
